{"kind":"table","sheet":"Prob","address":"A1:F20","rows":20,"cols":6,"values":[[null,null,null,null,null,null],["Let us consider two devices D1 and D2.  ",null,null,null,null,null],["The device D1 is made by three critical pieces a, b and c, such that even if only one of them is defective, then the device does not work. If the piece a is defective with probability Pa, and similarly Pb for piece b and Pc for piece c, what is the probability that the device D1 does not work?",null,null,null,null,null],["The device D2 is made by two critical pieces v and w, such that if at least one of them works, then the device works. If the piece v is defective with probability Pv, and similarly Pw for piece w, what is the probability that the device D2 does not work? ",null,null,null,null,null],["What is the maximum value of the probability of defects for piece a such that the probability that the device D1 does not work is lower or equal than the target probability Pt?",null,null,null,null,null],[null,null,null,null,null,null],["Pa",0.029,null,null,null,null],["Pb",0.0034,null,null,null,null],["Pc",0.0044,null,null,null,null],[null,null,null,null,null,null],["Probability that the device D1 does not work",null,null,null,null,0.03655927384000002],[null,null,null,null,null,null],["Pv",0.149,null,null,null,null],["Pw",0.127,null,null,null,null],[null,null,null,null,null,null],["Probability that the device D2 does not work",null,null,null,null,0.018923],[null,null,null,null,null,null],["Pt",0.02,null,null,null,null],[null,null,null,null,null,null],["Maximum value of the probability of defects for piece a such that the probability that the device D1 does not work is lower or equal than the target probability Pt?",null,null,null,null,0.012310800070984729]]}
